---
layout: layouts/content.njk
pagination:
  data: data
  size: 1
  alias: cafe
permalink: "catcafes/{{ cafe.name | slugify }}/"
---
<a class="is-4" href="/catcafes">‚Üê Back to List</a>
<h1 class="title is-1">{{ cafe.name }}</h1>
<h3 class="subtitle is-3">Find them at <a href="{{ cafe.link }}">{{ cafe.link }}</a></h3>
<div class="columns">
  <div class="column">
    <h5 class="title is-5 mb-0">Located at:</h5>
    <address>
      <p>{{ cafe.street1 }}</p>
      <p>{{ cafe.street2 }}</p>
      <p>{{ cafe.city }}, {{ cafe.state }}, {{ cafe.zipcode }}</p>
      <p>{{ cafe.country }}</p>
    </address>
    <br />
    <h5 class="title is-5 mb-1">Contact Info</h5>
    {% if cafe.email %}
      <p>Email: <a href="mailto:{{ cafe.email }}">{{ cafe.email }}</a></p>
    {% endif %}
    {% if cafe.phone_number %}
      <p>Phone: <a href="tel:{{ cafe.phone_number }}">{{ cafe.phone_number }}</a></p>
    {% endif %}
  </div>
  <div class="column">
  <h5 class="title is-5 mb-0">Hours</h5>
  <table class="table">
    <tbody>
      <tr><td>Monday:</td><td>{{ cafe.monday_hours }}</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Tuesday:</td><td>{{ cafe.tuesday_hours }}</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Wednesday:</td><td>{{ cafe.wednesday_hours }}</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Thursday:</td><td>{{ cafe.thursday_hours }}</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Friday:</td><td>{{ cafe.friday_hours }}</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Saturday:</td><td>{{ cafe.saturday_hours }}</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Sunday:</td><td>{{ cafe.sunday_hours }}</td></tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>

  <h5 class="title is-5 mb-1">Pricing</h5>
  {% if cafe.hour_price %}
	  <p>{{ cafe.hour_price }}</p>
  {% else %}
  <p>No info available</p>
  {% endif %}

  </div>
  <div class="column">
  <iframe class="map-top" width="598" height="450"
    src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed/v1/place?key=AIzaSyCTLaaSox94xKGtY2eQfybYbgcxz4LRv3Y&q={{ cafe.name | e }}{{ cafe.street1 | e}},{{ cafe.city | e }}, {{ cafe.state | e}}, {{ cafe.country | e }}"
 allowfullscreen></iframe>
  </div>
</div>
  <div>We do our best to make sure this information is accurate and up to date. The info displayed here is primarily there to give a general idea of the times and prices of the cafe you're looking at. We always recommend giving them a call to double check any info. Things change! We hope you enjoy your visit to your local (or not so local) cat cafe!
  </div>
